data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to 454 Cinnamon Drive, a beautiful and spacious home nestled in the*Gated* community of Tuscany Preserve. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home features an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or spending time with family. The kitchen boasts*Granite Counter* space, Closet Pantry and a breakfast bar, making it the ideal spot for whipping up your culinary delights. Downstairs also boast a laundry room and half bathroom. Upstairs includes all bedrooms. The primary bedroom is a peaceful oasis with an*En-suite Bathroom* and an extra large*Walk-in Closet*. The other bedrooms are bright and airy, offering plenty of space for relaxation, study or work office. The home also features a two patios, providing the perfect spots for enjoying the beautiful Florida weather. Exterior home pressure washing & painting, landscaping, irrigation, internet and cable tv are all included in monthly HOA fees. The community amenities include a clubhouse with fitness center, pool, hot tub, basketball/tennis courts and splash area. This home is just minutes away from Lake Marion, shopping and dining options.
